{"tid":2172880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"標榜「適合示威場合使用」嘅通訊軟件Bridgefy被發現漏洞超多","createTime":"2020-08-25T02:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T12:36:00.000Z","uid":131691,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"01401fb5cdab37bc63b2855dd4ed8a6331348618","tid":2172880,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:17:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/features/2020/08/bridgefy-the-app-promoted-for-mass-protests-is-a-privacy-disaster/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farstechnica.com%2Ffeatures%2F2020%2F08%2Fbridgefy-the-app-promoted-for-mass-protests-is-a-privacy-disaster%2F&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=00e00200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://arstechnica.com/features/2020/08/bridgefy-the-app-promoted-for-mass-protests-is-a-privacy-disaster/</a><br />\n<br />\n攻擊者可以：<br />\n1. 搵到你真實身份<br />\n2. Map哂成個地方有邊個同邊個講過嘢，幾時講過嘢<br />\n3. 解密direct messages<br />\n4. 假扮用戶身份<br />\n5. 斷咗成個網絡去<br />\n6. 直接MITM，唔淨止即時見到你send/receive啲咩，仲可以即時改你嘅messages<br />\n<br />\nRoyal Holloway嘅研究人員已經於4月通知咗Bridgefy公司，但係至今仍然無一個漏洞被fix。<br />\n<br />\n====================<br />\n<br />\n我記得呢個app喺連登有人推薦過，快啲uninstall啦。<br />\n真係要玩mesh networking嘅（驚斷網），用open source同埋已經被audit過嘅Briar啦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://briarproject.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbriarproject.org%2F&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=2383f4d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://briarproject.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好再推薦呢啲proprietary軟件啦~"},{"pid":"5af5a7587e8de5de9ff66c37423111ea79a69706","tid":2172880,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0fcdfedf49ec9c7772cc8af093d35026f173cc","tid":2172880,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n